* Auto-generated testbench for regulator feedback: U4
* Divider: R20/R21, ratio=0.1202
* Expected Vout=5.0V, Vfb=0.6010V (Vref=0.595V)
* Topology: standard
* Model: ideal passives (exact for DC divider)

VIN out_rail 0 DC 5.0
R20 out_rail fb_net 732k
R21 fb_net 0 100k

.control
op 
